N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 161.6 - Interest on overpayment

State Regulations

No interest on any net overpayment resulting from a
change of election under this Part will be allowed, provided the refund is made
within three months after the filing of New York State personal income tax
return or amended New York State personal income tax returns required by this

Part. Notes
